bucketsyncd (0.4.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Security fix: sanitize notification strings against command injection
  * Fix: outbound watcher goroutine no longer dies on first transient error
  * Fix: inbound AMQP reconnection busy-spin on closed channel
  * Fix: defer-in-loop resource leaks (file handles, contexts)
  * Fix: integer overflow in exponential backoff (gosec G115)
  * Deps: fsnotify, klauspost/compress, golang.org/x/{crypto,net,sys,text}

 -- Ross Golder <ross@golder.org>  Fri, 16 May 2026 11:25:00 +0000

